Search for an app on Flathub "flatpak search <name>"
Install app for current user "flatpak install flathub <app.id>"
Install app system-wide "sudo flatpak install flathub <app.id>"
List installed apps "flatpak list"
List user-installed apps only "flatpak list --user"
Run an installed app "flatpak run <app.id>"
Update all flatpaks "flatpak update"
Update user flatpaks only "flatpak update --user"
Uninstall a flatpak "flatpak uninstall <app.id>"
Uninstall for user only "flatpak uninstall --user <app.id>"
See info about a flatpak "flatpak info <app.id>"
List file access permissions "flatpak info --show-permissions <app.id>"
Set override for app "flatpak override <app.id> <option>"
Set user override (recommended) "flatpak override --user <app.id> <option>"
Remove override "flatpak override --reset <app.id>"
Remove user override "flatpak override --user --reset <app.id>"
Add Wayland socket permission "flatpak override --user <app.id> --socket=wayland"
Allow access to home folder "flatpak override --user <app.id> --filesystem=home"
Allow access to specific folder "flatpak override --user <app.id> --filesystem=/home/you/Videos"
Set env var for QT on Wayland "flatpak override --user <app.id> --env=QT_QPA_PLATFORM=wayland"
Add Flatpak remote (Flathub) "flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo"
List available remotes "flatpak remotes"
List installed runtimes and apps "flatpak list --app --runtime"
Remove unused runtimes "flatpak uninstall --unused"
